      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip rear differential, ensuring precise torque distribution. The chassis has been maintained to preserve its signature handling characteristics, including documented subframe reinforcement to enhance torsional rigidity. Recent mechanical attention includes a valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the internal tolerances are within factory specifications. This example offers a visceral, analog driving experience with a flat torque curve and an 8,000 RPM redline, presenting in honest, well-sorted condition.",
